SUMMARY:Common Threads—Community Cross Stitch with Open Heart
LOCATION:Fringe Boulevard\, King William St (between James St N and Hughson
  St N)\, Hamilton\, ON
DESCRIPTION:Company: Open Heart (Hamilton)\nGenre: Free Outdoor Events\, Fa
 mily Programming\nJoin in on the Cross Stitching progress with Open Heart 
 as they guide participants to build a large cross stitch design together! 
 A drop-in activity on the Boulevard during our first two full-length days\
 , come and stitch for a short time or a while! Open Heart facilitators are
  teaching participants how to cross stitch within the designed pattern the
 y are sharing on the Boulevard. Whether you’re already a cross-stitch pr
 o or want to try a new crafting technique\, we can’t wait to see your co
 ntributions! Together\, we’ll complete the full design—stitch by stitc
 h!\nGeneral Admission: FREE\nMore info: https://hftco.ca/events/common-thr
 eads-community-cross-stitch-with-open-heart/
URL:https://hftco.ca/events/common-threads-community-cross-stitch-with-open
 -heart/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
