SUMMARY:Beading Workshop w/ Beadwork by Kay
LOCATION:Fringe Boulevard\, King William St (between James St N and Hughson
  St N)\, Hamilton\, ON
DESCRIPTION:Company: HFTco (Hamilton)\nGenre: Free Outdoor Events\nShé:kon
 ! I'm Kaileigh and I am a Kanien'kehá:ka beadwork artist from Six Nations
  currently residing in Hamilton ON. I am the owner and Artist behind Beadw
 ork By Kay creating small batch Haudenosaunee beadwork and I have been a w
 orkshop facilitator for the last 3 years providing beadwork classes throug
 hout the GTA. I am passionate about teaching and sharing the art of beadwo
 rk from both a historical and contemporary perspective while creating a su
 pportive and creative space for all to enjoy!\nGeneral Admission: $15\nMor
 e info: https://hftco.ca/events/beading-workshop-w-beadwork-by-kay/
URL:https://hftco.ca/events/beading-workshop-w-beadwork-by-kay/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
